_sText:
Map by Prawn

Textures by Prawn


Info:

This is a rats styled xc/jump map, that on a scale from 1 to 10 in jump skillz takes about a 5 or 6 to complete.

The map had orginally 2 sponge boats in the zink and a ramp to make it possible for the boats to driver over the edge and down on the floor, but i couldn't get the boats working proberly so i had to delete them.
And the water on the floor and in the zink somehow bugged the map so i had to delete that too. :((
At the beginning the map also had a 3d skybox, but i deleted that to make it less laggy.

I would very much like to thank my friend PhQniX for testing the map over a 100 times, without him it wouldn't be done, and the jumps would be crap!

I started making the map a long time ago but because of some env_cupemap bug I kinda gave up on it untill now when i got it fixed and released!

I will proberly try to get som updates of this map out somtime with the boats and water.

At the end I there was supppose to be a driveable "paper plane" that could fly. But i had to trash that too :(

And the end you wil find a race track and a secret room. Containing funny stuff.

At the end outside the secret room you wil find hats that indicates you have completet the map, and ofc a teleport back to the map it self, for you being able to show off you fine new hat!

If you play the map and find any bugs at !all! i would be very happy if you would tell me :) 

The map it self looks a little like my kitchen irl. xD
